     Security Checklist

     - Backend API key restricted to Places API only
     - Frontend API key restricted by domain
     - API keys in .env (gitignored)
     - 30-day cache max (Google TOS)
     - "Powered by Google" attribution on all Google content
     - Rate limiting on review endpoints
     - Input validation on googlePlaceId field
     - HTTPS only for API calls
     - No Google review modification/scraping

