     ---
     Known Limitations

     1. Google API Limit: Max 5 reviews per request (Google restriction)
     2. Cache Duration: 30 days max (Google TOS requirement)
     3. Review Selection: Cannot control which 5 reviews Google returns
     4. Google Response: Cannot respond to Google reviews via API (use Google My Business)
     5. Place ID Changes: Rare but possible (admin can update)

